corder\\\"}]}\"}}],[\"$\",\"nav\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"Breadcrumb\",\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-1\",\"children\":[false,[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"className\":\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Home\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\",\"key\":\"mthhwq\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-chevron-right size-3.5 shrink-0\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Screen Recorder\"}]]}]]}]}]]\n1a:[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Free Screen Recorder — No Install, No Sign Up\"}]\n1b:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-lg text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Record your screen, window, or tab with webcam overlay and microphone — a free alternative to Loom. Everything runs in your browser.\"}]\n1c:[[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Person\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"James Nicolaus\\\",\\\"jobTitle\\\":\\\"Builder & Maintainer, Free Tool Shed\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"James Nicolaus builds and maintains every tool on Free Tool Shed. Each tool is designed, tested in real browsers across desktop and mobile, and shipped only after handling the messy edge cases — large files, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\\\",\\\"worksFor\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Free Tool Shed\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://freetoolshed.com\\\"}}\"}}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[\"Built and maintained by\",\" \",[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"href\":\"/about\",\"className\":\"font-medium text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline\",\"rel\":\"author\",\"children\":\"James Nicolaus\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]\n1d:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"Summary\",\"className\":\"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-4\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Free Tool Shed's Screen Recorder captures your screen, a window, or a browser tab with optional webcam picture-in-picture and microphone audio — all client-side via the MediaRecorder API. Trim the recording in-browser and export to WebM, MP4, or animated GIF. No upload, no sign-up, no time limit beyond your machine's memory. A free alternative to Loom and Vidyard.\"}]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"No Time Limits\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Loom's free plan caps you at 5 minutes per video. Here there are no caps, no watermarks, and no upload queue — record as long as your browser has memory.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Webcam Picture-in-Picture\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Drop your webcam into any corner as a circle or square bubble. The overlay is baked into the final video, ready to share.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Trim & Export\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Trim the start or end with draggable handles, then download as WebM (instant) or convert to MP4 / GIF in-browser. No uploads.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Your Video Stays Private\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"The recording is held in your browser tab's memory and never uploaded. Close the tab to wipe it — no servers, no accounts.\"}]]}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2a\",null,{}]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8 flex justify-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L16\",null,{\"slot\":\"mid-content\"}]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-16 space-y-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Free Screen Recorder Online — No Install, No Sign Up\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"You shouldn't have to create yet another account or install a 100 MB desktop app just to record a quick walkthrough. Free Tool Shed's Screen Recorder runs entirely in your browser — pick a quality preset, choose which audio to capture, optionally drop in a webcam overlay, and hit record. It works on Windows, macOS, Linux, Chromebooks, and even a locked-down work laptop where you can't install anything.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Unlike Loom (capped at 5 minutes and 25 videos on the free plan) or OBS Studio (powerful but a desktop install with a steep learning curve), this tool is built for the common case: record your screen, trim the ends, and download. Your video never leaves your browser — there are no servers, no accounts, and no upload queues. Export as WebM instantly, or convert to MP4 or GIF with an in-browser ffmpeg.wasm transcode. The whole thing is free, open, and ad-supported so it can stay that way.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Features\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Record full screen, a single window, or a browser tab\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"720p, 1080p, or 1440p quality presets at 30 fps\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"VP9 / Opus encoding when your browser supports it\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"System audio capture (tab audio in Chrome)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Microphone capture for narration\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Mix both audio sources in a single recording\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Optional webcam picture-in-picture overlay\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Choose any of four corners for the overlay\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Small / Medium / Large webcam sizes\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Circle or square webcam shape\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Overlay is baked into the final video\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"3-second countdown before recording starts\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Pause and resume without losing the clip\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Up to 2 hours per recording\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Live elapsed timer during recording\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Draggable trim handles on the timeline\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Keyboard nudges for frame-accurate trim boundaries\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Non-destructive trim — reset anytime\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Playback loops inside the trim window\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"childr