choose a screen, window, or browser tab to capture. In Chrome, check 'Share tab audio' if you want system sound from a tab. After a 3-second countdown, recording begins.\"}]]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"li\",\"3. Record, pause, and stop\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"3. Record, pause, and stop\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Click Pause to freeze the recording (the elapsed timer stops too) and Resume to pick it back up. When you're done, click Stop to finalize. There's no time limit beyond a 2-hour safety cap, and nothing is uploaded as you record — everything lives in your browser's memory.\"}]]}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"li\",\"4. Review and trim\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"4. Review and trim\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Play back your recording with the custom video player. Drag the two green handles on the timeline to cut the start or end. Use ← / → for 0.1s nudges, or hold Shift for 1-second steps. Home and End snap to the boundaries. Hit Reset trim anytime to restore the full range.\"}]]}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"li\",\"5. Export your recording\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"5. Export your recording\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Choose WebM for an instant download (no transcode, no waiting), MP4 for universal H.264 playback, or GIF for a palette-optimised animation. Give the file a name and click Download. MP4 and GIF lazy-load a ~30 MB ffmpeg core on first use — cached afterwards, so follow-up exports are much faster.\"}]]}]\n30:[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the Screen Recorder\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Pick the smallest capture region that still tells the story\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Pick the smallest capture region that still tells the story\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Full-screen recordings are the largest, the slowest to upload, and the hardest to watch on a phone. Pick a specific window or tab when the whole screen isn't necessary.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Enable system audio for app demos, mic for narration\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$30:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Enable system audio for app demos, mic for narration\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"App demos need the application's own sound (notifications, video output). Walk-throughs need your voice. The recorder lets you mix both — pick the right combination for your audience.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Trim before exporting\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$30:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Trim before exporting\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"The first few seconds (mouse moving to start) and last few seconds (mouse moving to stop) almost always need trimming. The built-in trim removes them without re-encoding.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Export WebM for the web, MP4 for sharing\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$30:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Export WebM for the web, MP4 for sharing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"WebM is smaller and renders directly in browsers — best for embedding. MP4 is more compatible with messaging apps, social platforms, and older players.\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Common Mistakes to Avoid\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\