",\"children\":\"How do I trim the start or end of my recording?\"}]\n46:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"After you stop recording, drag the two green handles on the timeline. The left handle sets the new start, the right sets the new end. Use ← / → for 0.1s nudges, Shift+← / → for 1-second steps, and Home / End to snap to a boundary. Trimming is non-destructive — hit Reset trim to restore the full range.\"}]\n47:[\"$\",\"details\",\"What export formats are supported?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"What export formats are supported?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"WebM (instant, no transcode — your browser already recorded in this format), MP4 (H.264/AAC for universal compatibility with Quicktime, Premiere, YouTube, and social platforms), and GIF (palette-optimised, capped at 12 fps and 720p width for sane file sizes). MP4 and GIF use ffmpeg.wasm locally — no upload, no server.\"}]]}]\n48:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Why is MP4 export slow the first time?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Why is MP4 export slow the first time?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"MP4 and GIF exports lazy-load ffmpeg.wasm on first use — that's about 30 MB of WebAssembly code served from unpkg.com and cached by your browser. Subsequent exports skip the download. WebM exports always skip ffmpeg entirely when the trim covers the full recording.\"}]]}]\n49:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Does my recording get uploaded anywhere?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Does my recording get uploaded anywhere?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"No. Everything runs client-side. The recording lives in your browser tab's memory (as a Blob), gets trimmed in-place, and downloads directly to your device. There are no servers, no cloud storage, and no analytics on the video content. Close the tab and the recording is gone.\"}]]}]\n4a:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Why would I use this instead of Loom?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Why would I use this instead of Loom?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Loom's free plan caps you at 5 minutes per video and 25 videos total, requires an account, and uploads your video to their servers. This tool has no time cap (beyond a 2-hour safety limit), no account, and no uploads. If you need Loom's sharing and commenting features, keep using Loom. If you just need to record and download, this is faster.\"}]]}]\n4b:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Why would I use this instead of OBS Studio?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Why would I use this instead of OBS Studio?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"OBS is vastly more powerful — scenes, sources, filters, streaming, plugins. But it's a desktop install with a learning curve. This tool is for the common case: hit record, trim, download. No install, no setup, no scenes.\"}]]}]\n4c:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I use this on a Chromebook or a work laptop?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I use this on a Chromebook or a work laptop?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Because it runs entirely in the browser, it works on Chromebooks, locked-down work machines, and anywhere a desktop install isn't possible. As long as your browser supports getDisplayMedia (Chrome 72+, Edge 79+, Firefox 66+), you're good.\"}]]}]\n26:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n4d:I[27201,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\"],\"IconMark\"]\n29:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Free Screen Recorder Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Record your screen, window, or tab with webcam overlay and microphone — right in your browser. A free alternative to Loom. No sign up required.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"google-adsense-account\",\"content\":\"ca-pub-7700405385978151\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"3\",{\"rel\":\"canonical\",\"href\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/screen-recorder\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Free Screen Recorder Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"5\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"Record your screen, window, or tab with webcam overlay and microphone — right in your browser. A free alternative to Loom. No sign up required.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"6\",{\"property\":\"og:url\",\"content\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/screen-recorder\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"7\",{\"property\":\"og:site_name\",\"content\":\"Free Tool Shed\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"8\",{\"property\":\"og:image\",\"content\":\"https://freetoolshed.c