"$L29\",\"$L2a\",\"$L2b\",\"$L2c\",\"$L2d\"]}]]}]}]]}]\n1a:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"details\",\"Is this screen recorder really free?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Is this screen recorder really free?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no premium tiers, no watermarks, and no sign-up required. The tool is ad-supported, which is how it stays free for everyone. Ads only appear outside the recording workspace itself.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Do I need to install anything?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Do I need to install anything?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"No. The entire recorder runs inside your browser using the MediaRecorder API, Web Audio API, and canvas compositing. There's nothing to download and nothing to uninstall. It works on any modern Chromium-based browser (Chrome, Edge, Brave, Opera) and Firefox.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"How long can I record?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"How long can I record?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Up to 2 hours per clip. The cap exists so the in-memory video buffer doesn't exhaust your browser's heap. For most use cases (tutorials, bug reports, walkthroughs) that's plenty of headroom. If you need multi-hour recordings, a desktop app is still the right tool.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Does it record system audio?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Does it record system audio?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes, on Chrome-based browsers you can capture tab audio or entire desktop audio. In the browser's share dialog, check 'Share tab audio' or 'Share system audio'. Firefox has more limited system audio support — microphone capture works everywhere.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I record with my webcam in the corner like Loom?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I record with my webcam in the corner like Loom?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Enable the Webcam Overlay in Setup, pick a corner, choose Small/Medium/Large, and switch between a circle or square bubble. The overlay is composited into the recording via a canvas, so it's baked into the final video — it'll look exactly the same when you download it.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I pause and resume a recording?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I pause and resume a recording?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Click Pause to freeze the recording — the elapsed timer stops too, and resuming picks up exactly where you left off. Most browser-based recorders don't let you pause at all.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"How do I trim the start or end of my recording?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\"]}],\"$L30\",\"$L31\",\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\"]}]]}]\n1d:null\n1e:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Recording at 4K when 1080p is plenty\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Most viewers watch screen recordings on a 1080p display. Recording at higher resolution just creates a heavier file with no visual benefit and longer trim/export times.\"}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Forgetting to disable notifications\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$18:1:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Forgetting to disable notifications\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"A Slack notification mid-demo is embarrassing and may leak private content. Enable Do Not Disturb before recording — every OS has a one-click toggle.\"}]]}]]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Exporting GIF for a 60-second recording\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$18:1:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Exporting GIF for a 60-second recording\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"GIF balloons in size past about 10 seconds and looks worse than equivalent video. Use MP4 or WebM for anything longer than a quick loop.\"}]]}]]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Closing the tab before saving\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$18:1:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Closing the tab before saving\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Recordings live in memory until you export. Closing the tab discards the recording — export first, close after.\"}]]}]]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-takeaways\",\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-takeaways\",\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Key Takeaways\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"The Screen Recorder captures screen, window, or tab with optional webcam picture-in-picture and microphone.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":[[\"circle\",{\"cx\":\"12\",\"cy\":\"12\",\"r\":\"10\",\"key\":\"1mglay\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\",\"key\":\"dzmm74\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-foreground\",\"children\":\"The Screen Recorder captures screen, window, or tab with optional webcam picture-in-picture and microphone.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Everything runs client-side via MediaRecorder; recordings stay in your browser until you export.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$22:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Everything runs client-side via MediaRecorder; recordings stay in your browser until you export.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Trim in-browser and export to WebM, MP4, or animated GIF.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$22:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Trim in-browser and export to WebM, MP4, or animated GIF.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"It is a free alternative to Loom and Vidyard with no time limit beyond your machine's memory.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$22:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-foreground\",\"children\":\"It is a free alternative to Loom and Vidyard with no time limit beyond your machine's memory.\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n23:[\"$\",\"td\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}]\n24:[\"$\",\"td\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}]\n25:[\"$\",\"td\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}]\n26:[\"$\",\"td\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"py-2  \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}]\n27:[\"$\",\"tr\",\"Microphone Audio\",{\"className\":\"border-b border-border/50\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Microphone Audio\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"py-2  \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}]]}]\n28:[\"$\",\"tr\",\"System / Tab Audio\",{\"className\":\"border-b border-border/50\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"System / Tab Audio\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"py-2  \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}]]}]\n29:[\"$\",\"tr\",\"Pause / Resume\",{\"className\":\"border-b border-border/50\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Pause / Resume\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"No\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"py-2  \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}]]}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"tr\",\"Trim Start / End\",{\"className\":\"border-b border-border/50\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Trim Start / End\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes (browser)\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Basic\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"py-2  \",\"children\":\"Yes\"}]]}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"tr\",\"Export Formats\",{\"className\":\"border-b border-border/50\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Export Formats\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\",\"children\":\"WebM / MP4 / GIF\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Cloud link only\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"MP4 download\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"MKV / MP4 / FLV\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"py-2  \",\"children\":\"MP4 / GIF / etc.\"}]]}]\n2c:[\"$\",\"tr\",\"Data Privacy\",{\"className\":\"border-b border-border/50\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Data Privacy\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Client-side only\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Uploaded to Loom\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Uploaded to Loom\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Local\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"py-2  \",\"children\":\"Local\"}]]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"tr\",\"Works on Chromebook\",{\"className\":\"border-b border-border/50\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Works on Chromebook\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes (web)\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"Yes (web)\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 \",\"children\":\"No\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"py-2  \",\"children\":\"No\"}]]}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"How do I trim the start or end of my recording?\"}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"After you stop recording, drag the two green handles on the timeline. The left handle sets the new start, the right sets the new end. Use ← / → for 0.1s nudges, Shift+← / → for 1-second steps, and Home / End to snap to a boundary. Trimming is non-destructive — hit Reset trim to restore the full range.\"}]\n30:[\"$\",\"details\",\"What export formats are supported?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"What export formats are supported?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"WebM (instant, no transcode — your browser already recorded in this format), MP4 (H.264/AAC for universal compatibility with Quicktime, Premiere, YouTube, and social platforms), and GIF (palette-optimised, capped at 12 fps and 720p width for sane file sizes). MP4 and GIF use ffmpeg.wasm locally — no upload, no server.\"}]]}]\n31:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Why is MP4 export slow the first time?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Why is MP4 export slow the first time?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"MP4 and GIF exports lazy-load ffmpeg.wasm on first use — that's about 30 MB of WebAssembly code served from unpkg.com and cached by your browser. Subsequent exports skip the download. WebM exports always skip ffmpeg entirely when the trim covers the full recording.\"}]]}]\n32:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Does my recording get uploaded anywhere?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Does my recording get uploaded anywhere?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"No. Everything runs client-side. The recording lives in your browser tab's memory (as a Blob), gets trimmed in-place, and downloads directly to your device. There are no servers, no cloud storage, and no analytics on the video content. Close the tab and the recording is gone.\"}]]}]\n33:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Why would I use this instead of Loom?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Why would I use this instead of Loom?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Loom's free plan caps you at 5 minutes per video and 25 videos total, requires an account, and uploads your video to their servers. This tool has no time cap (beyond a 2-hour safety limit), no account, and no uploads. If you need Loom's sharing and commenting features, keep using Loom. If you just need to record and download, this is faster.\"}]]}]\n34:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Why would I use this instead of OBS Studio?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Why would I use this instead of OBS Studio?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"OBS is vastly more powerful — scenes, sources, filters, streaming, plugins. But it's a desktop install with a learning curve. This tool is for the common case: hit record, trim, download. No install, no setup, no scenes.\"}]]}]\n35:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I use this on a Chromebook or a work laptop?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I use this on a Chromebook or a work laptop?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Because it runs entirely in the browser, it works on Chromebooks, locked-down work machines, and anywhere a desktop install isn't possible. As long as your browser supports getDisplayMedia (Chrome 72+, Edge 79+, Firefox 66+), you're good.\"}]]}]\n","/tools/screen-recorder":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[39756,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\"],\"default\"]\n3:I[37457,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\"],\"default\"]\n4:[]\n0:{\"rsc\":[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{}]}]]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":\"$W4\",\"buildId\":\"4HHM_hbHH_2OHNlzVJNpA\"}\n","/tools":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[24678,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/11~hh-yuwxxvh.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0s01892_~8u82.js\"],\"AdSlot\"]\n3:I[39756,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\"],\"default\"]\n4:I[37457,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\